ike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/195126_eaebc9c7158ce8535201e4ae6c072c6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F195126_eaebc9c7158ce8535201e4ae6c072c6b.jpg&h=1a8b18cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止袁某一個人出<br />\n所謂集腋成裘<br />\n<br />\n原來同一Set素材都有其他組織Share<br />\n<br />\n有心人反一地兩檢<br />\n<br />\n重奪話語權<br />\n<br />\n原來可以更簡單</blockquote><br />\n細組織仲勤力過班泛民大黨"},{"pid":"0e09c86a3ee4b9ec0428f6ac7becf2577cf6b15d","tid":357541,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/195126_eaebc9c7158ce8535201e4ae6c072c6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F195126_eaebc9c7158ce8535201e4ae6c072c6b.jpg&h=1a8b18cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止袁某一個人出<br />\n所謂集腋成裘<br />\n<br />\n原來同一Set素材都有其他組織Share<br />\n<br />\n有心人反一地兩檢<br />\n<br />\n重奪話語權<br />\n<br />\n原來可以更簡單</blockquote><br />\n細組織仲勤力過班泛民大黨</blockquote><br />\n細組織雖然資源唔多<br />\n但有心有力唔計算政治利益<br />\n<br />\n原本以為塊牌係A1 Size海報<br />\n<br />\n行近睇原來係紙張A4痴埋<br />\n<br />\n手作仔都做得好體面"},{"pid":"cf5414e1ce1e7f97e8e66d22a68c63429878387f","tid":357541,"uid":47774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"63ebbde13f57b05f390ffc5f61c7b8778d0e84fc","tid":357541,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5c3022a65abad6fc2bc4c96f8928ddda081b38","tid":357541,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13